ZH: 机舱里有很多座位。
EN: The cabin has many seats.

ZH: 机舱里有空调系统以保持舒适的温度。
EN: The cabin has an air conditioning system to maintain a comfortable temperature.

ZH: 机舱内有紧急出口。
EN: There are emergency exits inside the cabin.

ZH: 乘客必须在起飞前将手机放置在机舱模式。
EN: Passengers must put their phones on airplane mode before takeoff.

ZH: 安全扣带坐在机舱里的每个座位上。
EN: Safety belts are attached to every seat in the cabin.

ZH: 空中乘务员在机舱里分发食品和饮料。
EN: Flight attendants distribute food and drinks in the cabin.

ZH: 机舱内有一个婴儿座椅。
EN: There is a baby seat inside the cabin.

ZH: 飞机起飞后，乘客必须系好安全带直到达到巡航高度。
EN: Passengers must keep their seat belts fastened until the plane reaches cruising altitude.

ZH: 乘客在机舱里可以享受娱乐节目。
EN: Passengers can enjoy entertainment programs in the cabin.

ZH: 高级舱的机舱内设有豪华座椅。
EN: The cabin in the first class has luxurious seats.

ZH: 耳塞可供乘客在机舱里使用以降低噪音。
EN: Earplugs are available for passengers to use in the cabin to reduce noise.

ZH: 机舱内有应急人员和设备。
EN: There are emergency personnel and equipment inside the cabin.

ZH: 飞机起飞时，机舱门将被关闭。
EN: The cabin door will be closed during takeoff.

ZH: 乘客必须熄灭机舱内的所有电子设备。
EN: Passengers must turn off all electronic devices in the cabin.

ZH: 在飞行中，乘客可以自由进出机舱。
EN: Passengers are free to enter and exit the cabin during the flight.

ZH: 机舱内设有灭火器。
EN: Fire extinguishers are located inside the cabin.

ZH: 高级经济舱的机舱内设有脚踏座位。
EN: The cabin in premium economy class has footrest seats.

ZH: 机舱内有独立的卫生间。
EN: There are separate restrooms inside the cabin.

ZH: 在紧急情况下，机舱顶部会释放氧气面罩。
EN: In case of emergency, oxygen masks will drop down from the cabin ceiling.

ZH: 机舱内有咖啡和茶的自动售货机。
EN: There are vending machines for coffee and tea inside the cabin.
